parameters:
Cerburus Octopus: Eventually, I'll challenge you again and
take over this organization... But until you defeat Dynamite
Abalone and unify the city, I'll work for you as a lowly
underling... Hmph...

Memimi: Ah, I'll look forward to your revenge! But in the
end, I'll win again! Hahaha...

Cerburus Octopus: Tch... Acting all high and mighty... Even
after being forced to wear an erotic outfit and being made
to do a reverse rape scene on TV, you're still so full of
yourself...

Memimi: Could you not bring that up so much? It's something
I'm rather sensitive about...

Cerburus Octopus: That mayor has caused trouble for almost
every monster in Doritoku City... This isn't just your
problem or Shark Broccoli's anymore!! The entire city's
monsters are pinning their hopes on the match with Duke
Shark!!

Memimi: Of course, I understand... The responsibility is
immense. If we defeat him, the cause of this dark era...
there's no doubt it will be a huge step towards our long-
cherished wish!

Cerburus Octopus: Even my family's boxing gym has been hit
by the recession... At the very least, you've got to punch
him for me too. Listen, I'll teach you a boxer's punch...
with a one-two... come on!

Cerburus Octopus: Cough... Keep it up like that in the real
deal... *cough*

Memimi unleashed her inner ferocity, significantly boosting
her attack power...

Underling: When I joined the organization, I thought
unifying the city was impossible, but thanks to Lord Shark's
achievements, it's starting to feel real. If you never
forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: You must never give up on your dreams... I will
continue to fight as many times as necessary to achieve my
goal. You all should just believe in me and Lord Shark
Broccoli, and follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, seeing Lord Shark's numerous erotic
appearances was like a dream come true... The camera in the
shower room has been removed, but I've saved recordings for
days and watched them over and over... I know it's wrong,
but there's no way I can delete the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: To think the mayor would show up... I never
imagined it! That bastard, acting so brazenly...! And if we
lose, Lord Shark Broccoli making an AV debut?! I really want
to see it, but he's taking us lightly...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a personal gift from me! I bought it
with my own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As
someone involved in the powder refining business, no matter
what happens, I can't let the manufacturing method be passed
on...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. This powder, Lord Shark Broccoli's masterpiece, I
won't hand it over to anyone...

After eating the nutritious powder, you feel revitalized!
Max HP increased by 50!

Memimi: Shark Broccoli Boss... Only one more victory until
our long-cherished goal of unifying all the organizations in
the city. I will make it happen, even if it costs me my
life... Please look forward to it!

Shark Broccoli: Duke Shark... You have truly done well. You
are my pride and joy...

Shark Broccoli: However, you tend to take on everything by
yourself... It's not just about Monster Fights... No, in
fact, unifying all the organizations in the city isn't the
only path to peace. Sometimes it's important to rely on
those around you and think flexibly about the future...

Memimi: ...You may be right... But, Boss... This personality
of mine... I can't seem to do anything about it...

Shark Broccoli: ...The root of that personality of yours
probably stems from the trauma of when the orphanage you
grew up in was shut down, and no one was there to help
you... It pains my heart to think of how you felt back
then...

Shark Broccoli: ...I too have faced a great setback in the
past... I was left without help, lost my place... betrayed
by comrades... and dumped by a woman...

Shark Broccoli: There hasn't been a night I haven't
regretted that day... but now, having everyone in the
organization around me is truly a blessing. To achieve peace
in the city, what I can do alone is far too little...

Memimi: Boss, you are a wonderful person... Everyone here
has been saved by Shark Broccoli Boss, in big ways and
small. That's why we work as your hands and feet.

Shark Broccoli: Thank you... But the truth is... I don't
deserve to stand above everyone. When the city of Doritoku
becomes peaceful, I will reveal everything... and then,
there will be no place for me here...

Memimi: No matter what your past may be, there is no doubt
that Shark Broccoli Boss is a wonderful person!! Please
don't say such sad things...! No matter what we hear, we
will never forget the kindness we've received!!

Shark Broccoli: ...I'm sorry for making you anxious before
the match, Duke Shark... Let's leave this conversation here
for now. But remember, I made a vow that day...

Shark Broccoli: To return this asparagus to its rightful
place and atone for the sins we have committed...!
Memimi: Aspara... Huh? What were we talking about...?

Shark Broccoli: I'm sorry, Duke Shark... We've burdened you
with the negative legacy we caused... Mayor Orca... Orca
Asparagus was a junior in the pro wrestling organization I
used to belong to.

Memimi: I believe in you, Boss Shark Broccoli. No matter
what happened in the past, I know that you have always been
dedicated to everyone in the dark organization...

Shark Broccoli: Thank you, Duke Shark... It all started on
that day... It was all because of my wrong judgment that
everything happened... That day... when it all began...

Underling: Was it three years ago that Lord Shark was picked
up by the big boss? This organization was formed five years
ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
what happened at that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's a rapid rise... Now Lord Shark has become
one of the most important figures in the dark organization,
putting him on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I must repay is not only Lord Shark
Broccoli... but also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and sometimes guided me. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I can ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! You...
exposing my shame to close acquaintances... my personal
relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Sharky-san loses and has to make
an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I want
Sharky-san to be mine alone... I do want to see Sharky-san
having sex, but I don't want her to do it with anyone other
than me...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV raping celebrities in reverse, I felt like I was going to
lose it, and now to think she has to sleep around with other
men as a matter of routine... it does give me a bit of a
hard-on, but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel
but...

Underling: At least, take this...! It's a heart necklace
that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor Orca...!!

Memimi: Gross... I mean... uh, I'll just accept the
sentiment... thank you...

With the underling's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...

Anomalocaris: The next Monster Fight will determine who will
unify the city's dark organizations... It's so thrilling...
I really wanted to be the one to achieve it... but I have to
acknowledge your strength...

Memimi: Hehe, you've become quite honest, haven't you,
Anomalocaris... Just watch, I will surely defeat the final
formidable enemy and present the throne of Dirt City to Lord
Shark Broccoli!

Anomalocaris: Even after making you do a naked masturbation
run around the city, you didn't break and managed to get
your revenge, staying loyal to the boss... Maybe someone
like you is a true monster...

Memimi: Forget about that story... damn it... When you're a
monster of my level, such episodes are nothing to boast
about, they're just embarrassing to talk about... damn,
damn...

Anomalocaris: I remember... it was five years ago... I had
just graduated from high school, had a job lined up, and was
enjoying my spring break... But as soon as the mayor
changed, the company went under, and before the entrance
ceremony, I was decided to be unemployed...

Memimi: It's a heartbreaking episode... Everyone who joins a
dark organization has their life go awry somewhere, and when
they can't handle it anymore, they stray from the path...

Anomalocaris: Please... make him realize it for me too...!
My family runs a karate dojo... I'll teach you a move! Like
this... make your legs into an inverted 'V', and then,
tighten like this...

Anomalocaris: Hmm... with this, you could withstand even a
runaway locomotive! I'm counting on you... do your best...!

Memimi: I doubt it would work against a runaway express
train... but this technique will be useful. Thank you,
Anomalocaris...

Memimi's defense has greatly increased! Max HP increased by
300!

Underling: It seems Cerberus Octopus-sama has acknowledged
you and the big boss as his superiors... He'll never admit
it out loud, though. We, the former minions of Cerberus
Octopus, will also cooperate with all our might for the
unification of the city.

Memimi: That's reassuring... With the merger of our
organization and the Cerberus Octopus faction, we now have
over 100 members. Moreover, minor organizations are rushing
to join us to secure good positions while they can. In terms
of numbers alone, we're already the largest in the city...

Underling: It's all thanks to us spreading those videos of
Shark Duke all over the city in advance! That's what
explosively increased the city's attention...

Memimi: ...You've done something unnecessary... I really
wanted to collect the distributed DVDs, but it's too late
now... They've been copied far more than they were sold, and
have spread even outside the city...

Underling: It's been five years since the Orca Mayor took
office... His misrule continues, and the people who have
somehow endured are reaching their limit. For now, the
majority of citizens can still lead decent lives, but who
knows how long that will last...

Memimi: The chain of tragedies must be stopped here... He is
the worst monster spawned by this Mudgain City. If I don't
defeat him now, a future of ruin awaits all the citizens...

Underling: I used to be a subordinate of Lord Anomalocaris,
but now that I'm under you, I truly think it was the right
decision. If the city's underworld organizations are unified
and the conflicts cease, society should become better...

Memimi: The dark organizations are full of people with no
money, no education, and no jobs, but if everyone comes
together as one, what we can do will greatly increase. We
also need to think about various things for the city after
unification...

Underling: What exactly are you planning to do...? Even if
the city becomes peaceful, can you really live a decent life
after spreading uncensored masturbation videos all over the
world as the cost of victory...?

Memimi: Right now, I'm living a completely normal life, you
know? Just because people in the street point fingers at me
or I see my genitals all over the internet... it doesn't
change my life, does it?

Underling: I remember... right after the current mayor took
office, taxes skyrocketed... Road maintenance and public
services were drastically cut back. Many facilities were
closed, and a lot of stores were forced out by land
sharks...

Memimi: With the rise in unemployment, numerous dark
organizations and monsters emerged, marking the start of
Dirtown's dark age... I never imagined the day would come
when we'd fight the mayor who's the root of all this.

Underling: That mayor rarely makes public appearances, so
hardly anyone has seen him. I never would have guessed he
was a monster...

Memimi: To begin with, can you really just replace a mayor
by defeating him? I don't really understand the world of
politics...
